<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <wps:Execute
    xmlns:wps="http://www.opengis.net/wps/2.0" 
    xmlns:ows="http://www.opengis.net/ows/2.0" 
    xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" 
    xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" 
    xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.opengis.net/wps/2.0 ../wps.xsd" 

    service="WPS" 
    version="2.0.0" 
    response="document" 
    mode="sync"> 

    <ows:Identifier>de.hsbo.wacodis.forest_vitality_change</ows:Identifier> 
    
    <!-- Sentinel-2 file URL (Open Access Hub or CODE-DE) for first timestep-->
    <wps:Input id="OPTICAL_IMAGES_SOURCES_1">
        <wps:Data mimeType="text/plain">https://scihub.copernicus.eu/dhus/odata/v1/Products('21eb3657-9a68-46cf-979a-9b731dfedf24')/$value</wps:Data>
    </wps:Input>
    
    <!-- Sentinel-2 file URL (Open Access Hub or CODE-DE) for second timestep-->
    <wps:Input id="OPTICAL_IMAGES_SOURCES_2">
        <wps:Data mimeType="text/plain">https://scihub.copernicus.eu/dhus/odata/v1/Products('72bdd44c-bc96-406f-95ee-e6e903a59452')/$value</wps:Data>
    </wps:Input>
    
    <wps:Output id="PRODUCT" transmission="reference" mimeType="image/geotiff"/>
    
    <wps:Output id="METADATA" transmission="value" mimeType="text/json"/>
</wps:Execute>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<wps:Execute
	xmlns:wps="http://www.opengis.net/wps/2.0"
	xmlns:ows="http://www.opengis.net/ows/2.0"
	xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
	xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
	xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.opengis.net/wps/2.0 ../wps.xsd"
	
	service="WPS"
	version="2.0.0"
	response="document"
	mode="async">
	
	<ows:Identifier>de.hsbo.wacodis.gdal_warp</ows:Identifier>

	<wps:Input id="OPTICAL_IMAGES_SOURCE">
		<wps:Data mimeType="text/plain">https://scihub.copernicus.eu/dhus/odata/v1/Products('305585dc-7a22-4e40-9260-e19b9b804f36')/$value</wps:Data>
	</wps:Input>

	<wps:Input id="EPSG">
		<wps:Data mimeType="text/plain">EPSG:32632</wps:Data>
	</wps:Input>

	<wps:Output id="PRODUCT" transmission="reference" mimeType="image/geotiff"/>
	
	<wps:Output id="METADATA" transmission="value" mimeType="text/json"/>
	
</wps:Execute>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<wps:Execute
	xmlns:wps="http://www.opengis.net/wps/2.0"
	xmlns:ows="http://www.opengis.net/ows/2.0"
	xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
	xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
	xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.opengis.net/wps/2.0 ../wps.xsd"
	
	service="WPS"
	version="2.0.0"
	response="document"
	mode="sync">
	
	<ows:Identifier>de.hsbo.wacodis.land_cover_classification</ows:Identifier>

	<!-- URL for Sentinel-2 file (from Copernicus Open Access Hub or CODE-DE) -->
	<wps:Input id="OPTICAL_IMAGES_SOURCES">
		<wps:Data mimeType="text/plain">https://scihub.copernicus.eu/dhus/odata/v1/Products('1b469212-a1bd-4a7f-9d86-ebca495e597b')/$value</wps:Data>
	</wps:Input>
	
	
	<!-- Area of interest for Sentinel file -->
	<wps:Input id="AREA_OF_INTEREST">
		<wps:Data mimeType="text/plain">[5.87320, 55.00501, 5.87443, 55.00650]</wps:Data>
	</wps:Input>
	
	<!-- Training data -->
	<wps:Input id="REFERENCE_DATA">
    	<wps:Reference xlink:href="http://wacodis.eftas.com:8081/geoserver/wacodis/ows?service=WFS&version=1.0.0&request=GetFeature&typeName=wacodis%3AWaCoDiS_Landbedeckung_2019-10-14_unterklasse&maxFeatures=50&outputFormat=gml3&srsName=EPSG:32632" mimeType="text/xml" schema="http://schemas.opengis.net/gml/3.0.0/base/feature.xsd" />
	</wps:Input>
	
	<wps:Output id="PRODUCT" transmission="reference" mimeType="image/geotiff"/>
	
	<wps:Output id="METADATA" transmission="value" mimeType="text/json"/>
	
</wps:Execute>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<wps:Execute
	xmlns:wps="http://www.opengis.net/wps/2.0"
	xmlns:ows="http://www.opengis.net/ows/2.0"
	xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
	xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
	xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.opengis.net/wps/2.0 ../wps.xsd"
	
	service="WPS"
	version="2.0.0"
	response="document"
	mode="sync">
	
	<ows:Identifier>de.hsbo.wacodis.sealing_factor</ows:Identifier>

	<!-- Sentinel-2 file URL (Open Access Hub or CODE-DE) -->	
	<wps:Input id="OPTICAL_IMAGES_SOURCES">
		<wps:Data mimeType="text/plain">https://scihub.copernicus.eu/dhus/odata/v1/Products('24fcc458-fb43-4ca6-9a3e-b34c90781508')/$value</wps:Data>
	</wps:Input>
	
	<!--Vector data that should be used as masking layer-->
	<wps:Input id="MASKING_DATA">
    	<wps:Reference xlink:href="http://wacodis.eftas.com:8081/geoserver/wacodis/ows?service=WFS&version=1.0.0&request=GetFeature&typeName=wacodis%3Amask_befestigungsgrad&maxFeatures=50&outputFormat=gml3" mimeType="text/xml" schema="http://schemas.opengis.net/gml/3.0.0/base/feature.xsd" />
	</wps:Input>
	
	<wps:Output id="PRODUCT" transmission="reference" mimeType="image/geotiff"/>
	
	<wps:Output id="METADATA" transmission="value" mimeType="text/json"/>
	
</wps:Execute>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<wps:Execute
	xmlns:wps="http://www.opengis.net/wps/2.0"
	xmlns:ows="http://www.opengis.net/ows/2.0"
	xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
	xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
	xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.opengis.net/wps/2.0 ../wps.xsd"
	
	service="WPS"
	version="2.0.0"
	response="document"
	mode="sync">
    <ows:Identifier>de.hsbo.wacodis.wcs_test_algorithm</ows:Identifier>
    
    <!-- Sentinel-2 file URL (Open Access Hub or CODE-DE) -->	
    <wps:Input id="WCS_DATA">
        <!--wps:Data mimeType="text/plain">https://www.wcs.nrw.de/geobasis/wcs_nw_dgm</wps:Data-->
        <wps:Data mimeType="text/plain">https://www.wcs.nrw.de/geobasis/wcs_nw_dgm?VERSION=2.0.1&SERVICE=wcs&REQUEST=GetCoverage&COVERAGEID=nw_dgm&FORMAT=GTiff</wps:Data>
    </wps:Input>
    <wps:Input id="AREA_OF_INTEREST">
        <wps:Data mimeType="text/plain">[6.9,50.9,7.6,51.34]</wps:Data>
    </wps:Input>
    <wps:Output id="PRODUCT" transmission="value" mimeType="text/xml"/>
</wps:Execute>
